column2:
"Looks like it's over.
It is not necessary to confirm as the
silence says it all."

"How long can this peace and quiet last
at the seabed? I do not think it will last
very long though."

"I think there will be a chance to clean up
the mess again real soon so I’ll depend
on you again when the time comes."

"……終わったみたいだね。
確認しなくても静けさでわかる。"

"それじゃ、こいつが報酬だ。
おつかれさん。"

"この海底の静寂がいつまで続くか。
残念だがアタシは楽観できない。"

"すぐにまた掃除を頼むことになる気が
するけど、そのときはよろしくね。"
